<para> <image type="html" name="convex_hull.png"></image>
   Susan Hert and Stefan Schirra This package provides functions for computing convex hulls in two dimensions as well as functions for checking if sets of points are strongly convex are not. There are also a number of functions described for computing particular extreme points and subsequences of hull points, such as the lower and upper hull of a set of points. <linebreak/>
